org.iiitb.model.bean
Class DMU

java.lang.Object
  org.iiitb.model.bean.DMU

public class DMU
extends java.lang.Object

A memory unit(MemoryUnit) that is further divisible.

The subunits(UMU) are indivisible.

Typically this class should be sub classed to suit the specific memory management scheme being designed, viz, paged segmentation, segmented paging or kernel memory management scheme
